Hello **{{officer_name}}**,<br/>

{{#if (eq entity_kind "Punishment")}}

{{#if (eq removed "Yes")}}
This message serves notice of your removal from the Tactical Firearms Unit. This decision wasn't made in a hurry, an in depth investigation and discussion have taken place and TFU Command have deemed your actions do not represent the qualities we expect from our members of this Unit. The reason for this removal is the following:
{{else}}
This message serves notice of the removal of your {{old_certification}} certification, following this inbox you will have the {{new_certification}} certification. This decision wasn't made in a hurry, an in depth investigation and discussion have taken place and TFU Command have deemed your actions do not represent the qualities we expect from our TFOs.
{{/if}}
<br/><br/>

<b>What happened: **{{what_happened}}**</b><br/>
<b>Disciplinary grading: **{{grading}}**</b><br/>
<b>Points issued:
{{#if (eq grading "1")}}
1
{{else if (eq grading "2")}}
2
{{else if (eq grading "3.1")}}
3
{{else}}
4
{{/if}}
</b><br/>
<b>Date of point expiry: **{{expiry_point}}**</b>
{{else}}
This message serves notice of the removal of your {{old_certification}} certification.
{{#if (eq removed "Yes")}}
Following this inbox you will be removed from the Tactical Firearms Unit as you are no longer qualified due to your demotion from {{old_rank}}.
{{else}}
Following this inbox your {{old_certification}} certification will be removed as you are no longer qualified due to your demotion from {{old_rank}}.
{{/if}}
{{/if}}<br/><br/>

{{#if (eq blacklist "Yes")}}
Following this decision, you will receive a <b>{{blacklist_length}} blacklist</b> from applying to any role within the Tactical Firearms Unit.<br/><br/>
{{/if}}

{{#if (eq entity_kind "Due to rank")}}
Feel free to reapply for the {{old_certification}} application again once you have reached the required qualifications.<br/><br/>

If you wish to dispute this disciplinary action, you may do so by directing a helpdesk to TFU and the Head of TFU will deal with it.
{{else}}
If you wish to dispute this disciplinary action, you may do so by directing a helpdesk to TFU and the Head of TFU will deal with it. If this punishment was decided from an Internal affairs complaint that you are actively disputing, the punishment will remain until the verdict is decided. At which point the decision of the dispute will dictate whether it is removed or not.
{{/if}}<br/><br/>

<b>Regards,</b><br/>
Lieutenant Tyler Bounce<br/>
Staff Sergeant Vina Yin<br/>
